{"title":"UPC. Criterios de ingreso","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/UCI-Medicina Crítica/UPC. Criterios de ingreso-2026.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"CRITERIOS DE\\NINGRESO UPC","guid":"Of6Wq5KNxcGCBvB8vnvbew","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"ESTRUCTURA DE LA UPC","guid":"VcEfEsiCz0iJw9JRlS36OQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"DEFINICIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Continuum de cuidados críticos → Sala ↔ UTI ↔ UCI","guid":"4txgAmTErU-444HERh7uOQ","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"Sistema integrado bajo dirección única (intensivista)","guid":"qHwN6ym-C0WU5e9-UEstEw","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"Flujo bidireccional según gravedad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"COMPONENTES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"UCI (Unidad de\\NCuidados Intensivos)","guid":"_5SHx_Gx_06_AdseIG8Jdw","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Soporte vital avanzado → VM invasiva, DVA, TRRC, ECMO","guid":"mrATjMapbkecMysK7HNYog","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"Monitoreo invasivo → Swan-Ganz, PIC","guid":"h_Fui2mJo0q_kZUN6gm2ig","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"Ratio enfermera:paciente → 1:1 a 1:2","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"6","text":"UTI (Unidad de\\NTratamiento\\NIntermedio)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"Sinónimos → IMC, step-down, HDU, high dependency unit","guid":"iGNbRoP2Ek6JBdHvtJkpXw","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"Monitoreo continuo SIN soporte vital avanzado","guid":"zQzXeqNpPUu4cjJMjKDppQ","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"VMNI, CNAF, telemetría","guid":"sq6mBRyK8kez-EszAEnDpQ","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"11","text":"Ratio enfermera:paciente → 1:3 a 1:4","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"1","text":"MODELOS ORGANIZACIONALES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"INTEGRADO → UTI dentro UCI, mismo equipo (recomendado DIVI)","guid":"xcgcF__TwUec_UN16DeC7Q","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"PARALELO → UTI adyacente, gestión común","guid":"7BOUm-xlPEOdTvdihohQYg","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"INDEPENDIENTE → UTI separada (↑ mortalidad si no hay UCI en hospital)","guid":"796FHGOT8Ei4FcrjYLio8A","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"1","text":"UNIDADES ESPECIALIZADAS","guid":"","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"UCC → SCA, arritmias complejas, IC severa, post-procedimientos","guid":"zS1OEJhdnke2fqSYzkTDKQ","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"Stroke Unit → ACV isquémico/hemorrágico, post-trombolisis","guid":"tV_9_JctO0ysdT6Z0R_Cgg","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"Unidad Weaning → weaning prolongado >7d, TQT, rehabilitación respiratoria","guid":"rwvIB5RxCEqEam7uUFb1-A","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"20","text":"Unidad Quemados → quemaduras extensas, manejo hidroelectrolítico","guid":"_RpZAb2CFUWOMaW8agrb1Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"0","text":"CLASIFICACIÓN INTERNACIONAL\\NNIVELES DE CUIDADO","guid":"erfEKnpmIkSI05Lpyb9OYQ","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"ICS UK 2021","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"NIVEL 0 → Sala general, CSV c/12h, ratio 1:6-8","guid":"5sWUn62dSEioD7lhTgVbgQ","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"NIVEL 1 → Enhanced care, riesgo\\Ndeterioro, CSV c/4-6h, ratio 1:4","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"NIVEL 2 → HDU/UTI, soporte UN órgano\\N(excepto VM invasiva), ratio 1:2","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"26","text":"NIVEL 3 → UCI, soporte ≥2\\Nórganos, VM invasiva, ratio 1:1","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"25","text":"WFSICCM 2016","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"NIVEL 1 UCI → hospitales pequeños/rurales,\\Nsoporte cardiorrespiratorio corto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"NIVEL 2 UCI → VM corto plazo\\N<24-48h, hospitales intermedios","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"NIVEL 3 UCI → espectro\\Ncompleto, VM prolongada,\\NTRRC, ECMO, rol académico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"25","text":"DIVI Alemania 2023","guid":"","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"NIVEL 1 → falla orgánica\\Núnica, VM limitada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"NIVEL 2 → cuidado\\Ncompleto mayoría pacientes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"35","text":"NIVEL 3 → todas especialidades,\\NECMO, hospitales universitarios","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"0","text":"PRINCIPIOS DE ADMISIÓN","guid":"WfnmZ2onMEGgA_O5V4694Q","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"PRINCIPIO FUNDAMENTAL","guid":"","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Paciente DEBE beneficiarse\\Ndel cuidado intensivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"Dos extremos SIN beneficio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"Too well to benefit → riesgo bajo, no\\Nrequiere intervención UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"Too sick to benefit → muerte\\Ninminente, irreversible","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"40","text":"Edad NO es criterio de\\Nexclusión per se","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"40","text":"Autonomía del paciente →\\Ndirectivas anticipadas, voluntad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"39","text":"MODELO PRIORIZACIÓN\\NSCCM (5 NIVELES)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"PRIORIDAD 1 → MAYOR","guid":"","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"Críticamente enfermo + inestable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"Requiere soporte vital → VM,\\NDVA, monitoreo invasivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"ALTA probabilidad recuperación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"48","text":"Sin limitación esfuerzo\\Nterapéutico, acepta RCP","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"47","text":"PRIORIDAD 2","guid":"","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"Requiere monitoreo intensivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"Potencial deterioro → podría\\Nnecesitar intervención inmediata","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"47","text":"PRIORIDAD 3","guid":"","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"Críticamente enfermo, BAJA\\Nprobabilidad recuperación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"Acepta UCI pero NO RCP","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"47","text":"PRIORIDAD 4","guid":"","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"Estable, candidato UTI o stepdown","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"59","text":"Generalmente NO se\\Nbeneficia de UCI","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"47","text":"PRIORIDAD 5 → MENOR","guid":"","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"Terminal o moribundo →\\Ncuidados paliativos","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"0","text":"ALGORITMO DE EVALUACIÓN","guid":"XJn6iszyVkWc0Z_1kleixQ","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"PASO 1 → IDENTIFICAR\\NDETERIORO AGUDO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"NEWS2 ≥5 → respuesta urgente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"NEWS2 ≥7 → alto riesgo,\\Nconsiderar ingreso UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"qSOFA ≥2 → evaluar sepsis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"65","text":"Cualquier parámetro score 3 en\\NNEWS → evaluación urgente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"64","text":"PASO 2 → EVALUAR\\NBENEFICIO POTENCIAL","guid":"","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"¿Requiere intervención\\NSOLO disponible en UCI?","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"¿Es reversible la condición aguda?","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"¿Cuál es el estado funcional\\NBASAL? (2 semanas previas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"70","text":"¿Existe limitación esfuerzo\\Nterapéutico previa?","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"64","text":"PASO 3 → ESTRATIFICAR\\NFRAGILIDAD (≥65 años)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"CFS 1-3 → no frágil,\\Nbeneficio esperado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"CFS 4 → vulnerable,\\Nevaluar caso a caso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"75","text":"CFS 5-6 → frágil\\Nleve-moderado (HR 1.34\\Nmortalidad)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"75","text":"CFS 7-9 → frágil severo/terminal,\\Ndiscutir proporcionalidad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"64","text":"PASO 4 → COMUNICAR\\NY DOCUMENTAR","guid":"","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"Informar paciente/familia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"Discutir objetivos de cuidado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"Registrar justificación en ficha clínica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"64","text":"DECISIÓN FINAL","guid":"","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Beneficio esperado + objetivos\\Nalineados → INGRESAR","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"Sin beneficio o confort\\Nprioritario → NO INGRESAR","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"84","text":"Incertidumbre → trial\\N48-72h + reevaluar","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"0","text":"PARÁMETROS\\NOBJETIVOS DE\\NINGRESO","guid":"8wukVauW4EOS2pc6ZQ1w0Q","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"SIGNOS VITALES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"FC <40 o >150 lpm","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"PAS <80 mmHg o caída\\N>20 mmHg basal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"89","text":"PAM <60 mmHg","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"89","text":"PAD >120 mmHg","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"89","text":"FR >35 rpm →\\NPREDICTOR\\NIMPORTANTE","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"88","text":"LABORATORIO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"Na <110 o >170 mEq/L","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"K <2.0 o >7.0 mEq/L","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"PaO2 <50 mmHg","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"95","text":"pH <7.1 o >7.7","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"95","text":"Glicemia >800 mg/dL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"95","text":"Calcio >15 mg/dL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"95","text":"Nivel tóxico drogas/químicos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"88","text":"IMAGENOLOGÍA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"Hemorragia cerebral con\\Nalteración conciencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"Aneurisma aórtico disecante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"103","text":"Ruptura visceral","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"0","text":"CRITERIOS POR\\NSISTEMA/PATOLOGÍA","guid":"Txiwa2il5E2Wkvo8HpYKbQ","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"CARDIOVASCULAR","guid":"","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"IAM con arritmias o\\Ninestabilidad → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"Shock cardiogénico → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"ICC con falla respiratoria → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"108","text":"Emergencia hipertensiva → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"108","text":"Post PCR → UCI SIEMPRE","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"108","text":"Taponamiento cardíaco → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"108","text":"Bloqueo AV completo → UCI","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"107","text":"RESPIRATORIO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"Falla respiratoria aguda\\Nrequiriendo VM → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"116","text":"FR >35 rpm → predictor\\Nrobusto necesidad UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"116","text":"PaO2/FiO2 <300 → SDRA\\Nleve, considerar UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"116","text":"PaO2/FiO2 <200 → SDRA\\Nmoderado, UCI indicada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"116","text":"PaO2/FiO2 <100 → SDRA\\Nsevero, UCI urgente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"116","text":"VMNI con mala respuesta\\N1-2h → escalar a UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"116","text":"Embolia pulmonar con\\Ninestabilidad → UCI","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"107","text":"NEUROLÓGICO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"HSA →\\NUCI/neurointensivo\\NSIEMPRE","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"124","text":"ACV con alteración\\Nconciencia → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"124","text":"Status epiléptico → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"124","text":"TEC severo GCS ≤8 → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"124","text":"Coma cualquier etiología → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"124","text":"Monitoreo PIC requerido → UCI","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"107","text":"SEPSIS/SHOCK SÉPTICO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"qSOFA ≥2 → evaluar para UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"Lactato >4 mmol/L → considerar UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"Necesidad DVA → UCI SIEMPRE","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"131","text":"NEWS ≥5 en sospecha\\Ninfección → respuesta urgente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"107","text":"GASTROINTESTINAL","guid":"","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"Hemorragia digestiva masiva → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"Falla hepática fulminante → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"136","text":"Pancreatitis severa → UCI","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"107","text":"ENDOCRINO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"Cetoacidosis diabética severa → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"Estado hiperosmolar → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"140","text":"Crisis tiroidea/adrenal → UCI","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"107","text":"QUIRÚRGICO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"Postoperatorio inestable → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"Cirugía mayor en frágil →\\Nconsiderar UCI 24-48h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"Cirugía\\Ncardíaca/neurocirugía\\Nmayor → UCI","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"107","text":"INTOXICACIONES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"Alteración conciencia +\\Ninestabilidad → UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"Riesgo arritmias (QTc\\Nprolongado) → UCI","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"0","text":"NO ADMITIR A UCI","guid":"TNKoAUKwzEy_67PCQeTItA","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"TOO WELL TO BENEFIT","guid":"","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"Cirugía vascular periférica estable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"CAD estable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"ICC leve","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"Sobredosis consciente sin riesgo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"152","text":"Postoperatorio sin complicaciones","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"151","text":"TOO SICK TO BENEFIT","guid":"","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"Daño cerebral severo irreversible","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"158","text":"Falla multiorgánica irreversible","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"158","text":"Cáncer metastásico sin\\Nrespuesta a tratamiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"158","text":"Estado vegetativo persistente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"158","text":"Paciente que rechaza\\Ncuidados intensivos","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"164","parent":"0","text":"SCORES DE ALERTA TEMPRANA","guid":"xLbdtzltBUawzC2DBxQhxw","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"NEWS2 → GOLD STANDARD","guid":"","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"7 parámetros → FR, SpO2, O2,\\NT°, FC, PAS, conciencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"165","text":"Rango 0-18 puntos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"165","text":"AUROC 0.90 para muerte/UCI en 24h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"165","text":"UMBRALES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"0-4 → bajo riesgo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"5-6 → riesgo medio,\\Nrespuesta urgente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"169","text":"≥7 → alto riesgo,\\Nrespuesta\\Nemergencia/UCI","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"165","text":"LIMITACIONES EN ANCIANOS","guid":"","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"AUROC ↓ de 0.77 a 0.\\N69 en ≥65 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"SUBESTIMA riesgo en ≥80 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"173","text":"\"Normal para NEWS\" puede ser\\N\"anormal para ESE paciente\"","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"177","parent":"165","text":"SOLUCIÓN → NEWS2 + edad o\\NNEWS2 + CFS (AUROC 0.77-0.86)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"178","parent":"164","text":"MEWS","guid":"","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"5 parámetros → PAS, FC,\\NFR, T°, conciencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"178","text":"MEWS ≥5 → ↑\\Nsignificativo riesgo\\Nrelativo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"178","text":"MEWS ≥7 → umbral óptimo\\Npost-deterioro agudo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"164","text":"qSOFA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"183","parent":"182","text":"3 parámetros → FR ≥22, PAS\\N≤100, alteración conciencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"182","text":"≥2 puntos → sospecha sepsis,\\Nevaluar disfunción orgánica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"182","text":"NEWS superior a qSOFA para\\Npredicción mortalidad","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"186","parent":"0","text":"CLINICAL FRAILTY SCALE (CFS)","guid":"V_Gts1Nha0qm2E-eUtlz-Q","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"APLICACIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"Evaluar al PRIMER CONTACTO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"187","text":"Estado basal 2 SEMANAS\\NPREVIAS a enfermedad aguda","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"187","text":"Puede obtenerse de familia/cuidador","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"187","text":"Tiempo aplicación <2 minutos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"187","text":"Alta confiabilidad interobservador","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"186","text":"ESCALA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"CFS 1-3 → no frágil","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"CFS 4 → vulnerable (NO IGNORAR)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"CFS 5-6 → frágil leve-moderado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"193","text":"CFS 7-9 → frágil severo/terminal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"198","parent":"186","text":"VALOR PRONÓSTICO EN UCI","guid":"","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"Factor pronóstico INDEPENDIENTE","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"CFS ≥5 en ≥65 años → HR\\N1.34 mortalidad UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"198","text":"Cada punto CFS → ↑ ~19%\\Nriesgo mortalidad 6 meses","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"198","text":"Mortalidad hospitalaria puede\\Nsuperar 30% en CFS altos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"198","text":"~40% sobrevivientes UCI egresan con\\Nnueva dependencia funcional","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"204","parent":"186","text":"LIMITACIONES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"205","parent":"204","text":"NO validado en <65 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"204","text":"NO usar en discapacidad\\Nestable (ej: parálisis cerebral)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"204","text":"NO reemplaza VGI completa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"204","text":"Puede subestimar\\Nfragilidad en obesos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"209","parent":"186","text":"IMPLICANCIA CLÍNICA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"210","parent":"209","text":"CFS ≥5 → umbral para\\Ndiscusión proporcionalidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"209","text":"NO es criterio exclusión automático","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"209","text":"Informa pero NO determina decisión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"209","text":"EVITAR dicotomización →\\Nriesgo es CONTINUO","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"214","parent":"0","text":"CONSIDERACIONES\\NGERIÁTRICAS EN UPC","guid":"Qyd-dzwwaEOliPb8f2XiMA","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"DECISIÓN UCI vs UTI EN ANCIANO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"216","parent":"215","text":"CFS 1-4 → evaluar\\Ncomo adulto general","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"215","text":"CFS 5-6 → considerar\\NUTI primera línea si","guid":"","children":[{"id":"218","parent":"217","text":"Condición potencialmente reversible","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"217","text":"No requiere soporte vital invasivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"217","text":"Objetivos compatibles\\Ncon cuidados activos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"221","parent":"215","text":"CFS 7-9 → UTI raramente indicada","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"222","parent":"214","text":"SÍNDROMES\\NGERIÁTRICOS\\NRELEVANTES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"Fragilidad → prevalencia\\N~30-40% en >65 años UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"222","text":"Multimorbilidad →\\NCharlson para cuantificar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"222","text":"Deterioro cognitivo → IQCODE\\Nbasal, ↑ riesgo delirium","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"222","text":"Sarcopenia → movilización\\Nprecoz para prevenir","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"222","text":"Malnutrición → MNA-SF, albúmina <3.\\N5 g/dL predictor mortalidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"222","text":"Polifarmacia → revisión\\Nobligatoria, deprescripción","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"214","text":"BUNDLE ABCDEF","guid":"","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"Estrategia con MAYOR\\NEVIDENCIA prevención delirium\\NUCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"229","text":"Relación DOSIS-RESPUESTA → mayor\\Ncumplimiento = mejores outcomes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"229","text":"Dexmedetomidina >\\Nbenzodiacepinas (↓ delirium)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"229","text":"Movilización precoz\\Nsegura incluso con VM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"229","text":"SAT + SBT\\Ncoordinados → ↓ días\\NVM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"229","text":"CAM-ICU 2x/día MÍNIMO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"229","text":"Intervenciones NO\\Nfarmacológicas PRIMERO","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"237","parent":"214","text":"PICS (POST-INTENSIVE\\NCARE SYNDROME)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"238","parent":"237","text":"Deterioro cognitivo post-UCI →\\Ntan severo como Alzheimer leve\\No TEC moderado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"237","text":"Delirium en UCI → predictor POTENTE\\Ndisfunción cognitiva largo plazo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"237","text":"Mayor recuperación funcional primeras 6\\NSEMANAS → ventana intervención","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"237","text":"Después 6 semanas →\\Nplateau funcional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"237","text":"Frágiles CFS ≥5 → mortalidad\\Nhasta 34% a 6 meses","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"237","text":"Solo ~50% ancianos \"sanos\"\\Nsobreviven 12 meses post-UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"237","text":"Depresión/ansiedad/TEPT →\\N~30%/30%/20% prevalencia","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"245","parent":"0","text":"CRITERIOS DE EGRESO UCI","guid":"1zH5eXW0cUyMFQIrSJOf-w","children":[{"id":"246","parent":"245","text":"PRINCIPIOS GENERALES","guid":"","children":[{"id":"247","parent":"246","text":"Estabilidad hemodinámica sin DVA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"246","text":"Vía aérea segura, sin VM o\\Nweaning completado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"246","text":"GCS >13 o basal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"246","text":"Diuresis >0.5 mL/kg/h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"246","text":"Sin necesidad monitoreo\\Ninvasivo continuo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"252","parent":"245","text":"TIMING DE EGRESO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"253","parent":"252","text":"Alta nocturna → ↑ riesgo\\Nreadmisión y mortalidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"252","text":"Alta fin de semana → ↑\\Nriesgo readmisión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"252","text":"Evitar alta <48h post-weaning VM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"252","text":"NEWS al alta >7 → alto riesgo\\Ndeterioro 24h (S 93.6%, E 82.2%)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"257","parent":"245","text":"FACTORES RIESGO READMISIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"Tasa readmisión general → 7%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"257","text":"Readmisión <72h →\\Nindicador calidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"257","text":"Mortalidad readmitidos\\N→ 2-10x mayor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"257","text":"PREDICTORES → SAPS III\\Nalto, ingreso desde sala, uso\\NDVA, estadía prolongada","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"262","parent":"0","text":"TOMA DE\\NDECISIONES Y\\NFUTILIDAD","guid":"9y6paDpopE2Z6EjkDKLI_g","children":[{"id":"263","parent":"262","text":"PRINCIPIOS","guid":"","children":[{"id":"264","parent":"263","text":"Edad SOLA → NUNCA\\Ncriterio de futilidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"263","text":"Futilidad = fragilidad severa +\\Nfuncionalidad pobre + discordancia valores","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"263","text":"SDM debe ser\\NANTICIPADA → antes de\\Ncrisis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"263","text":"Trial UCI 48-72h → estrategia\\Nválida cuando incertidumbre","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"263","text":"Cuidados paliativos PRECOCES\\N→ pueden ser paralelos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"263","text":"Retirar y no iniciar →\\Néticamente EQUIVALENTES","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"270","parent":"262","text":"DOCUMENTACIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"271","parent":"270","text":"Documentar\\NINCERTIDUMBRE → es\\Nhonesto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"270","text":"Planificación anticipada cuidados →\\Nreduce ingresos no beneficiosos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"270","text":"Modelo VALUE →\\Ncomunicación efectiva\\Nfamilias","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"274","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas ⭐","guid":"gqc7Q22DGUuV_vyk3fV5Gg","children":[{"id":"275","parent":"274","text":"FR >35 rpm → predictor\\Nrobusto necesidad UCI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"274","text":"NEWS ≥7 al alta UCI → postergar\\Nalta, alto riesgo deterioro 24h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"274","text":"CFS evaluar estado BASAL 2\\Nsemanas previas, NO actual","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"274","text":"CFS ≥5 factor independiente mortalidad UCI,\\Npero NO exclusión automática","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"274","text":"Overtriage > undertriage →\\Npreferible error hacia más cuidado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"274","text":"NEWS2 SUBESTIMA riesgo ≥80\\Naños → ajustar umbral mental","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"274","text":"CFS + NEWS2 → mejor\\Npredicción que cualquiera solo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"274","text":"Preocupación clínica sin score\\Nalto → ESCUCHARLA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"274","text":"Delirium hipoactivo → frecuente ancianos,\\Nfácil de perder, buscar activamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"274","text":"\"Hacer todo\" a veces significa \"hacer\\Ndaño\" → comunicar a familias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"274","text":"Conferencia familiar <72h en evento\\Ninesperado → puede ↑ TEPT","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"274","text":"Scores pronósticos (APACHE, SOFA) → NO\\Nusar solos para decidir ingreso","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"287","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"288","parent":"287","text":"1. Nates JL et al. ICU Admission, Discharge, and Triage Guidelines. Crit Care Med. 2016;44(8):1553-602.","guid":"aIfj8KddOUydcQU9t8qUNg","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"287","text":"2. ICS. Levels of Care Consensus Statement. UK. 2021.","guid":"Ip30tYMQPUqGwl0AV21kjA","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"287","text":"3. DIVI. Recommendations ICU Structure. Germany. 2023.","guid":"JUASX0gTyEud6g0F1eCgBA","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"287","text":"4. Bruno RR et al. CFS and mortality in older ICU patients. Ann Intensive Care. 2023;13:36.","guid":"iT0d3jZu80SVPqk6ngBX4w","children":[]},{"id":"292","parent":"287","text":"5. Suh GJ et al. CFS in nonagenarians. Crit Care. 2025;29:45.","guid":"X6kP2KfHkkWBPx4o7zwrcg","children":[]},{"id":"293","parent":"287","text":"6. Chung HS et al. CFS improves NEWS2, qSOFA, REMS. Sci Rep. 2025;15:8721.","guid":"cv0G4VqmfkCVwWD73CMC0g","children":[]},{"id":"294","parent":"287","text":"7. Bae JH et al. NEWS2 performance in elderly. Am J Emerg Med. 2025;78:112-8.","guid":"OVGxodNGDUWKRd8TqaFW3Q","children":[]},{"id":"295","parent":"287","text":"8. Nissen SK et al. NEWS2 underestimates risk in ≥80y. Ann Emerg Med. 2022;79(5):467-77.","guid":"F1WY5pMIIUGnkR3bj-h8Jg","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"287","text":"9. Pun BT et al. ICU Liberation Collaborative. Crit Care Med. 2019;47(1):3-14.","guid":"cRutGuVxh0GdyK4j4eHfPQ","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"287","text":"10. Herridge MS, Azoulay E. Outcomes after critical illness. N Engl J Med. 2023;388(10):913-24.","guid":"9XrLR0kt7kepV9LyGOPgTA","children":[]},{"id":"298","parent":"287","text":"11. Beil M et al. ESICM Consensus Very Old Patients. Intensive Care Med. 2025;51(1):89-104.","guid":"mmLdw-XEakq00tGQznCwfQ","children":[]},{"id":"299","parent":"287","text":"12. Flaatten H et al. VIP-1 Study. Intensive Care Med. 2017;43(12):1820-8.","guid":"h-2JRnQK8USTFgC9VPrYyQ","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":299,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"UCI/Medicina Crítica","folder":"Entidades clínicas/UCI-Medicina Crítica","filename":"UPC. Criterios de ingreso-2026","id":"map_2358","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"UPC. Criterios de ingreso-2026"}